CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 28, 1953, pg. 17 reads: "Platform Guests... A section of the speakers platform is shown as the program got under way Monday night at the citizens birthday testimonial for Mrs. Robert L. Vann...P.L. Prattis, executive editor of the Courier and general chairman of the party; Mrs. Toki Schalk Johnson, mistress of ceremonies; Mrs. Vann, William G. Nunn, managing editor of the Courier;...and Judge Lois McBride..."
TitMainTitle: Jessie Vann standing at microphone on stage, with P. L. Prattis, Toki Schalk Johnson, Bill Nunn Sr., and Lois McBride, in ballroom of the Penn Sheraton with sunburst patterned curtains, for Jessie Vann's birthday party
